data.description: Have you been looking for a beautiful home on 0.47 acres?! Your search has ended with this inviting, ranch style home located in the highly sought after Cornerstone neighborhood! You will be immediately greeted through the contemporary entryway into the living room. Imagine cozy nights around the fireplace with plenty of space to entertain guests. The kitchen boasts plenty of cabinet storage made complete with a dining room area. Down the hall you will find two guest bedrooms that share a spacious bathroom. The primary bedroom boast plenty of space with an oversized walk-in closet. In the primary bathroom you will find a garden tub with a separate shower. Outside, enjoy a screened in porch with a separate patio space.  The backyard has endless opportunities for gardening and ample space for outdoor activities! Did I mention there is a garage?! Situated just minutes from I-20 providing quick and easy access to Columbia and surrounding areas. This is a home you do not want to miss, so schedule your showing today!
